{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"substring","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/substring","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath Reference</a></b>: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT elements</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT functions</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath functions</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath axes</a>\n</div>\n<p>The <code>substring</code> function returns a part of a given string.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">substring(string, start)\nsubstring(string, start, length)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"arguments","title":"Arguments","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"string\"><code>string</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The string to evaluate.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"start\"><code>start</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The position within <code>string</code> the substring begins</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"length\"><code>length</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      The length of the substring.\n      If omitted, the returned string will contain every character from the <code>start</code> position to the end of <code>string</code>.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"Returns","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A string.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notes","isH3":true,"content":"<p>As in other XPath functions, the position is not zero-based. The first character in the string has a position of 1, not 0.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"Defined","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/1999/REC-xpath-19991116/#function-substring\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.2</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko support","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Supported.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"The substring function returns a part of a given string.","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:38:45.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"substring","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"substring","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"substring","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"substring","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/xpath/functions/substring","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/xpath/functions/substring/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/f22e42182591e38590c9add80de91a51bce3cde2","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/substring","title":"substring"}],"pageTitle":"substring - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}